title: Himitsu Sentai Momoider
description: Momo Sakura, 22, lives alone in Tokyo. Her profession: she is the Pink Momoider and is part of the Secret Combat Troops Momoider, a group of super sentai heroines! Unfortunately, the little girl is clumsy and her transformations often results in real fiascos...
